// ────────────── Output (Monitor) Configuration ──────────────
// https://github.com/YaLTeR/niri/wiki/Configuration:-Outputs
//
// This file is a per-machine placeholder.
// Run `niri msg outputs` to list your displays, then uncomment
// and rename the output blocks below for your specific setup.
//
// Example:
//   output "eDP-1" { scale 1.5; }
//   output "DP-3" { mode 2560x1440@144; position x=0 y=0; }
//
// Use /- to uncomment a block:
// /-output "eDP-1" {
// /-    scale 1.5
// /-}
